{"tid":2050101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"實驗功能：回覆負評過多，自動縮略顯示","createTime":"2020-06-04T02:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T10:01:38.000Z","uid":66260,"like":16,"dislike":129,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9c45b41e08648557f31a29715023dca0dcd780b0","tid":2050101,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我們留意到部份會員，故意搶先在多個主題發表令人反感之留言引人注意，或回覆與主題無關之內容影響正常討論。針對個別惡意影響討論的回覆，我們嘗試推出此實驗性功能作為測試。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如單一回覆符合以下「所有條件」，將會被自動縮略顯示，用戶需按一下才能觀看該回覆內容。<br />\n1. 暫時只於「時事台」及「政事台」試行<br />\n2. 回覆時間超過 30 分鐘<br />\n3. 回覆並非由樓主發表<br />\n4. 回覆負評多於 200 個，及佔正負評總和多於 90%</span><br />\n<br />\n有關本實驗性功能，我們將會持續觀察及收集意見，並因應情況修改條件。<br />\n若本功能帶來無法估計之負面影響，我們將會考慮取消。</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過work唔work?"},{"pid":"0e47d62f0a6873c312549a6047beb01469e70934","tid":2050101,"uid":162268,"like":5,"dislike":315,"score":-310,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"請負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3208d703746b1b895e68066a5256bb62090e792","tid":2050101,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:12:21.000Z","msg":"樓主回覆唔計<br />\n有冇白老鼠自願俾人負評留言?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ed3d64ae0a715643cf3ce49e52dff6e41a26ab","tid":2050101,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0e47d62f0a6873c312549a6047beb01469e70934","tid":2050101,"uid":162268,"like":5,"dislike":315,"score":-310,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"請負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as